    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "Been reading all sorts of posts about the best ways to develop workflows for Fable and it reminds me of how little we actually know about the best ways to organize work for long-running agents. Nobody has enough experience or has done enough testing to reach any real conclusions.",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/emollick/status/2072539615836213387",
    "time": "2026-07-02 12:35",
